<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbded756a-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s6992k"><num value="6992k">§ 6992k.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Administrator such sums as may be necessary for each of the fiscal years 1989 through 1991 for purposes of carrying out activities under this subchapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbded756b-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/89/272/tII/s11011">Pub. L. 89–272, title II, § 11011</ref>, formerly § 11012, as added <ref href="/us/pl/100/582/s2/a">Pub. L. 100–582, § 2(a)</ref>, <date date="1988-11-01">Nov. 1, 1988</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/102/2958">102 Stat. 2958</ref>; renumbered § 11011, <ref href="/us/pl/105/362/tV/s501/h/1/B">Pub. L. 105–362, title V, § 501(h)(1)(B)</ref>, <date date="1998-11-10">Nov. 10, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/3284">112 Stat. 3284</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbded756c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbded756d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idbded756e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/89/272/s11011">section 11011 of Pub. L. 89–272</ref> was renumbered section 11010 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s6992j">section 6992j of this title</ref>.</p>
